name: Dubidoso
description:
thoughtfully...

I think that over-thinking can influence the way you think.

- no kidding

how can I fit those thoughts inside my head?

usually good thoughts arrive at me thru the ear channel, with eyes closed.

- To me is the oposite, I need to cover my ears to think.

I like to think with my skin, naked, at the shower.

Maybe think with my nose, over some nice and warm coffee fumes...

- don't worry about all this, just go with your intuition
